<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.1.6">
<l>vāḻntārkaḷ vāḻntatu māmaḻai mokkuḷiṉ māyntumāyntu</l>
<l>āḻntāreṉ ṟallā laṉṟu mutaliṉ ṟaṟutiyā</l>
<l>vāḻntārkaḷ vāḻntē niṟpareṉ patillai niṟkuṟil</l>
<l>āḻntār kaṭalpaḷḷi yaṇṇa laṭiyava rāmiṉō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is no living [on] for those who have lived except for thinking</l>
<l>that they sink, vanishing, vanishing like bubbles in the great rains. There being an end without beginning,</l>
<l>there is no saying those who have lived, having once lived will last. If [you want] to experience lasting,</l>
<l>be servants of the majesty on the ocean bed, those immersed [in him].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
